{"tid":2194860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【檢測大龍鳳】雷鼎鳴：不參加者「唔係好市民」 應不獲政府派錢兼無份打疫苗","createTime":"2020-09-08T19:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T16:08:11.000Z","uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d615c2969696726d3068d2e11e67ac5fa7448484","tid":2194860,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T19:19:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/FXULU4SAQFCURAEZURYKHITGNQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=telegram\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FFXULU4SAQFCURAEZURYKHITGNQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtelegram&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNfZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=ce832240\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FFXULU4SAQFCURAEZURYKHITGNQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtelegram&h=9a7f5318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/FXULU4SAQFCURAEZURYKHITGNQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=telegram</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府硬推所謂普及社區檢測計劃，至今有約131萬人預約登記，被質疑勞民傷財無效抗疫。科大經濟學系前系主任雷鼎鳴指政府措施不夠嚴厲，建議日後再推行普及檢測時，可給予參加者獎勵，包括將檢測與健康碼掛鈎，或讓參與者優先接種疫苗；又建議若政府將來再「派錢」（回水），亦應只給曾參與檢測者：「其他嗰啲人佢唔係好巿民，派錢唔需要畀佢。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26jixgc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26jixgc.gif&h=bb4c25f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67a108b276547bb5511e7147c6b5e8119319bbbe","tid":2194860,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T19:21:37.000Z","msg":"俾佢大到添 即刻報左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74059708d5be7215be64e6d65fc2e082b292a223","tid":2194860,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T19:4